---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Philosophy" description="Why I log my technical work publicly.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[900px] px-6 py-16 gxsc-reveal">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-light tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-8 font-display">Philosophy</h1>

    <div class="space-y-12 gxsc-reveal gxsc-delay-1">
      <p class="text-xl text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        This is not a traditional portfolio. This is a <strong>Technical Workshop</strong>.
      </p>

      <section class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="section-header">The Goal</h2>
        <p>
          As an engineer and manager, I believe the most valuable asset is not the code you've written, but the <strong>process</strong> you've developed. 
          I use this site to publicly document my daily "Ships" and "Learnings."
        </p>
        <p>
          By logging my technical journey in real-time, I create a searchable archive for myself and a transparent record of my technical growth for others.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="section-header">What You'll Find Here</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Logs:</strong> Raw, daily updates on what I built and what I learned.</li>
          <li><strong>Essays:</strong> Long-form reflections on systems, management, and philosophy.</li>
          <li><strong>Wiki:</strong> A collection of resources, frameworks, and technical guides.</li>
          <li><strong>Work:</strong> A dashboard of current and past engineering projects.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="section-header">Professional Background</h2>
        <p>
          If you are looking for my resume, official bio, or professional contact info, please visit my primary landing page:
        </p>
        <a href="https://victorem.me" class="inline-block text-[var(--color-accent)] font-medium hover:underline">victorem.me →</a>
      </section>

      <div class="pt-8 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 gxsc-reveal gxsc-delay-2">
        <a href="/logs" class="btn btn-primary text-center">
          Read the Logs
        </a>
        <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-secondary text-center">
          Read Essays
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
